{"title":"莲花盛开的时候","authors":["杨忠义"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":12,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"莲花盛开的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨忠义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太久，太久"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次被迫无奈的出走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让母亲守望的瞳仁里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叠印上四百多个春秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今，你终于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到了自家门口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太远，太远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次坎坷艰辛的飘流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让母亲思念的长臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸向万里之遥的欧洲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今，你终于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"返航到自家码头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实，孩子，你走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走不出自家的院畴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子，其实，你飘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘不出母亲的双眸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下母子日夜牵手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是割不断的骨肉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子，你没有错"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必愧疚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因当年异域水手蛮横"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而母亲过于积弱贫瘦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是一只滴血的手印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为强人占领的借口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子，你没有变"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你心依旧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月斑驳的古炮台作证"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方的“蒙特卡洛”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河、长江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远在你血管里奔流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一个起自春天的构想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于结出成熟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在新世纪的晨曦里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在莲花盛开的时候"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}